      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative solver residuals converge to <1e-6 for all load steps; energy balance checked at each increment.",
      "rationale": "Newton-Raphson iterations converge to force residuals below 1e-6 for all 15 load increments in each simulation. Energy balance errors are below 0.01%. No spurious hourglassing or contact penetration detected."
