      "rationale": "The validation activities use the same device (non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw), the same test standard (ASTM F1717 static compression-bending), the same material (Ti-6Al-4V), and the same loading regime as the COU. The validation scenario is therefore directly representative of the intended use, and no extrapolation is required."
